This implementation of linked list includes the following methods:
- `insert(data)`: adds a new node with the specified data to the end of the list.
- `remove(key)`: removes the first occurrence of the specified key from the list.
- `search(key)`: returns True if the specified key is present in the list, otherwise returns False.
- `display()`: prints the elements of the linked list.
